                                    <span class="text-gray-700">Sueldo de Julio <span class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-medium">(incl. 1% aumento)</span>:</span>
                                    <span id="resSueldoJulio" class="font-semibold font-mono"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-md">
